[0.1.0]
====================

1.  +   Overhaul of data structure with an object-oriented feel [Improv]
            *   Links can be easily added to the addon by:
                * add a link entry into "presets.js" 
                * use the id (from the newly-created entry above) in locale files to 
                    provide a translation
2.  +   Added a background image on the panel [Improv]
3.  +   Added a hotkey for quickly creating a quick link [Improv]
4.  =   Graceful migration from v0.0.2 to v0.1.0 [Bug]
5.  +   More preset icons: (3 new) [Improv]
            + Foursquare
            + JSFiddle
            + Trello


[0.0.2]
====================

1.  +   More light-weight 
	        * Unrequired Jquery Files have been deleted
	        * Non-minified css and js in both Bootstrap and Font Awesome Library 
	            have been removed
2.  +   Semantic Versioning Enforcement [Improv]
	        * First-run shows the correct addon version
3.  +   Compatibility specification in First-run.html corrected for accuracy 
                [Improv]
4.  +   Version updated in package.json [Improv]
5.  =   Links in first-run.html removed [Bug]
	        * The images were wrapped in Links with href attr pointing to the images dir
	        * However the Link was "dead". Image didn't show up
6.  +   Font-Awesome upgraded to 4.1.0 [Improv]
7.  +   More preset icons:  (15 new) [Improv]
            + Apple
            + Codepen
            + Drupal
            + Git
            + Google
            + Pinterest
            + SoundCloud
            + Stack Exchange
            + Stack Overflow
            + Steam
            + Tumblr
            + Vimeo
            + Windows
            + Wordpress
            + Yahoo
8.  +   More custom icons: (2 new)
            + comments
            + cutlery
            + flag
            + institution
            + paper-plane



[0.0.1]
====================
1.  +   Icons added [Improv]
            * icon.png(48 x 48) and icon64.png(64 x 64) have been added
2.  +   Package.json updated for icons and semantic versioning [Improv]
3.  =   Holder.js in Bootstrap is removed [Bug][Secur]
4.  =   HTML Insertion.  [Bug][Secur]
            *Security measure
            *Ineffeciency
            *All .innerHTML += operations are now handled with jQuery's .append() a$
            *All .innerHTML -= operations are now handled with jQuery's .remove()
            *No more usanitized html. The elements required are created using docum$

5.  +   Compatibility Tested [Improv]
            * 21.0a - 32.0

Validation Results: https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/developers/upload/e14fb93a$

